headline.main: US Renews Global Terrorism Warning for Americans Abroad
headline.print_headline: US Renews Global Terrorism Warning for Americans Abroad

lead_paragraph: The State Department has renewed its global terrorism warning for American citizens abroad, urging them to stay vigilant in public places and boost their security awareness.
